A special luminous effect of unknown origin was observed on Norway.
The Russian Ministry of Defence finally acknowledged yesterday that near the borders with Norway it tested an intercontinental ballistic missile.
The launch failed again. The missile, previously designated to be the pride of the Russian army, is becoming the nightmare of Russian generals and Prime Minister Vladimír Putin.
