New urban space is created, provided with many green areas, probably from the computer-generated graphics of the designer.
For the rail transport system the S21 is harmful.
The transit station and the road support are designed for the transport of people, which was attributed to the enormous growth typical of the 1980s.
At that time there was no competition for low-cost flights.
But modern transport policy must first focus on strengthening freight transport, as rail transport is considerably more environmentally friendly than road haulage.
However, the new sections under construction are good for freight trains due to the intense gradients.
Even more serious is that the S21 also indirectly affects many other railway projects.
More than six billion euros must be buried in the Zuavos.
That's the official figure.
Experts consider it to be more realistic between ten and fifteen billion.
It is certain that in the next decade the money will be missing in other crossings and narrow passages on the net.
